* Command line arguments
--name --> to pass a custom name to the suite
--argumentfile --> to give a suite file argument that contains a list of robot tests

--settag
 -- to group test cases say, database related/production related/development related etc.
--pythonpath, to add python library paths during runtime
--listener
  --- start_suite (that runs before every suite starts running)
  --- end_suite (that runs after every suite completes running)
  --- start_test
  --- end_test
  https://robotframework.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/doc/userguide/RobotFrameworkUserGuide.html#listener-interface-method-signatures